name: Pink & Green Bait Bag Clutch
description:
Inspired by a Lobsterman's bait bag, this clutch was created using the same marine-grade material. Durable, yet ultra chic, this clutch is ready for wherever life takes you. 

Screen printed hot pink netting pattern with algae green stripe down the middle matches an algae green interior. Approximately 13x6". 

Hand printed and sewn in Portland, ME.
